svg.title: Arms of the University of Melbourne

g.desc:
Azure a figure intended to represent Victory robed and attired proper the dexter hand holding a Wreath of Laurel Or between four Stars of eight points two in pale and two in fess Argent
Postera crescam laude - "Grow in the esteem of future generations"
